title: Coast to Coast AM - Aug 07 2013 - Astral Travel - Planet X
description:
Date:	08-07-13
Host:	George Noory
Guests:	Dr. Bruce Goldberg, Marshall Masters
News segment guest: James McCanney

Hours 1 & 2: Hypnotherapist Dr. Bruce Goldberg talked about such topics as astral travel, out-of-body travel, teleportation, and his techniques for soul plane ascension, and "superconscious mind tap." 

Hours 3 & 4: Author and publisher Marshall Masters shared his contention that 'Planet X' is continuing its inbound path in our solar system, drawing closer to Earth.
